00:54.616 --> 00:55.716
[squawks]

02:00.394 --> 02:01.427
[car door closes]

03:25.118 --> 03:27.119
[paper rustling]

03:54.548 --> 04:04.482
<font color="#ffff00">Sync by honeybunny</font>
